long_description: at regis retail we are crazy about giving our customers amazing service and introducing them to amazing products. we have many years' experience in online retail for other companies, software development in online technologies, online internet marketing, new product design & development and experience of working with manufactures and suppliers all over the world. regis retail was founded as a central hub to create and launch various inhouse niche product brands. we have a deep understanding of what works but we also have the courage to introduce new things or old things in a new way. our passion for the customer experience together with our passion for technology will enable us to deliver incredible value to customers through amazing customer service leveraged from implementing the latest software on our websites and back systems for an efficient and high-quality offering to consumers across the uk and the world. we see it as our mission to serve the king in every way we can. above all else, any web property or brand that we create will always look to add value and not remove value from the customers experience.
